parameters.name: 10日常パート・放課後等落ち着いたシーン

parameters: Yui: "Sorry, \n[6]! Have you been waiting long?"

Yui: "You're right~, it's especially hot today... everyone's thinking
the same thing."
\n[6]: "Well, let's get in line for now!"
Yui: "Oh no! I forgot my sunscreen."
Karen: "You're with Amasawa-kun. Is this a date?"

Yui: "Ah, no... not a date per se, just thought we'd go to the pool
together because it's so hot, right \n[6]?"
Karen: "I heard you forgot your sunscreen?"
Yui: "Yeah, I thought I put it in my bag... I'm such a klutz..."
Karen: "If you want, you can use mine?"
Karen: "Of course. I brought five extras."
Karen: "UV rays are the archenemy of my beautiful skin, after all."
Karen: "Here you go. Take it! You don't need to return it."
Yui: "No, it's not that. Did you come to the pool alone, Saionji-san?"
Karen: "Yes, that's right. There's no man worthy of me at the moment."

parameters.name: 19恋愛パート・恋人との会話

parameters: Yui: "Then come have fun with us!"

Yui: "The more the merrier! Fun things are even more fun with more
people!"
\n[6]: "Yeah! Since we're all here, let's enjoy it together!"

Yui: "Come on, don't just stand there spacing out! Come join us and
let's line up together!"
Karen: "...Just saying how hot the summer is, that's all..."
Yui: "What's that, it's obvious, isn't it? Fufu."
\n[6]: "Saionji-san is surprisingly natural and funny. Hahaha."
Karen: "Huh? Amasawa-kun, did you just notice my hidden charm?"

Karen: "The sun is burning so fiercely, and maybe our love will flare
up this summer too?"

Yui: "It's hot because it's summer, if you stick too close you'll get
even hotter and shrivel up!"
Yui: "You hate the heat, don't you~. Right, \n[6]?"
